name: 𝘃𝟮.𝟬𝟬𝟬𝟯𝟵𝗯
description: Visual animated abstract texture generated using different generative tools and plugins, animated at 60fps  in a 1000x1000 px resolution. The holder of one of these editions (without selling it) earns a ticket (1 per tez wallet adress)  to a raffle for 50% of all the editions that are sold as a tez prize and a custom nft animated digital artwork when the burning takes place and all players get locked on the pool (each artwork lasts 1 week)
